{
  "sourceLanguage" : "ja",
  "strings" : {
    "" : {

    },
    "「敬語」ボタンの変換のしかたを変えたり、よく使う言い換えを自分のボタンとして追加できます。設定の「プロンプト」からいつでも編集できます。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "You can change how the “Keigo” button converts text, or add frequently used rephrasings as your own buttons. Edit them anytime from “Prompts” in Settings."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "你可以更改“敬语”按钮的转换方式，或将常用的改写添加为自己的按钮。可随时在设置的“提示词”中编辑。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「敬語」ボタンの変換内容を自分好みに編集" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Edit how the “Keigo” button converts to your liking"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "按你的喜好编辑“敬语”按钮的转换内容"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "%@回書き直し" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "%@ rewrites"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "%@ 次重写"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "※ お試し用の入力欄です。入力した文章はどこにも送信されません。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "* This is a trial input field. What you type is not sent anywhere."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "* 这是试用输入框。你输入的内容不会发送到任何地方。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "© 2026 敬語ボタン" : {

    },
    "10キー入力" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
